    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Long Description</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dinner invitation turns into a deadly game of wits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you arrive at a mysterious manor for an elegant meal, the doors lock behind you. Guests turn to statues, voices whisper through the walls, and the host’s motives grow more sinister with every course. You’re not here to eat… you’re here to solve your way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 Cinematic Escape-Room Puzzles – Each handcrafted challenge ties into the mystery, from cryptic logic problems to mechanical contraptions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎬 Movie-Style Storytelling – Fully integrated cinematics reveal characters, motives, and hidden clues.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 Interconnected Clues – Every puzzle is part of a bigger web; solutions hint at the truth behind the dinner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌗 Evolving Atmosphere – Shift from warm candlelit curiosity to tense, shadow-filled uncertainty as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 Immersive Audio &amp; Feedback – Custom voice acting, ambient soundscapes, and visual cues reward your every breakthrough.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you uncover the truth before the final course is served? Or will you become part of the manor’s collection?</p>",
